  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Evaluation of the combination of lateral femoral cutaneous nerve &quot;single shot&quot; and femoral
      nerve &quot;single shot&quot; block as effective and safe alternative postoperative analgesic
      technique after hip replacement surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
